These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different games are played: go, domino, mah-jongg
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, march, june
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, coffee
City: liverpool, san-francisco, boston
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, azalea, balloon-flower
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, mauve, coral
 1. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
 2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 4. the person playing domino is the person drinking milk##1
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is the person playing go##1
 8. the person who likes fuchsia is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person who likes coral##2
10. the person who likes fuchsia is in an odd position##4
11. the person who's birthday is in january is the person traveling to boston##1
12. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who likes mauve##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |         2          |     3      |
| Game          | go   | mah-jongg            | domino     |
| Birthday           | january | june | march |
| Beverage   | 7up      | coffee               | milk        |
| City           | boston        | liverpool         | san-francisco   |
| Flower         | balloon-flower     | azalea      | marigold       |
| Color     | coral        | mauve              | fuchsia       |

