.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, climbing, water-polo
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, puzzles, dancing
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, cain, bolivar
City: prague, san-francisco, miami
There are 3 different favourite colors: puzzles, azure, coral
3 different games are played: go, billiard, monopoly
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is the bolivar-smoker##1
 2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 3. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person traveling to prague##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the blend-smoker##2
 6. the person who likes puzzles is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person playing go##2
 7. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person who likes azure##1
 8. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person traveling to miami is the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |
| Sport      | swimming | climbing | water-polo        |
| Hobby          | puzzles   | dancing    | hiking        |
| Cigar   | blend    | cain | bolivar |
| City   | miami   | prague  | san-francisco         |
| Color           | coral    | puzzles | azure       |
| Game     | billiard   | monopoly    | go  |

