City: berlin, san-francisco, venice
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, march, april
 1. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
 2. the person driving the train is the art-deco house##1
 3. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person playing monopoly##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the palace house is between the fonseca-smoker and the person who's birthday is in march##2
 6. the art-deco house is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 7. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4
 8. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
 9. the person driving the train is on the far right##1
10. the old-henry-smoker is in an odd position##4
11. the fonseca-smoker is the person driving the bike##1
12. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
13. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3       |
| Game      | monopoly        | bridge     | chess          |
| House          | wooden     | palace | art-deco    |
| Cigar         | fonseca    | tiparillo  | old-henry |
