 7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
 8. the owner of the goldfish is the person who growsbegonia##1
 9. the electrician is in an odd position##4
10. the entrepreneur is in an even position##4
11. the firefighter is on the far left or far right##3
12. the tower house is the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
