10. the person playing snooker is the person driving the boat##1
11. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
12. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| City      | paris    | marseilles   | san-francisco   |
| Color          | pink    | amber    | lavender |
| Game   | domino       | snooker   | billiard    |
| Cigar   | bluemaster    | pall-mall | tiparillo  |
| Transport           | bike      | boat    | scooter       |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | writing  | board-games   |

