 7. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
 8. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 9. the person who growsorchid is the person who's birthday is in september##1
10. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3

