There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, tea, fanta
House: palace, futuristic, ranch-style
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, emerald, black
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, car, taxi
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, june, september
 1. the person drinking tea is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 2. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing go##1
 3. the person who likes black is the person playing backgammon##1
 4. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 5. the person drinking milk is in an even position##4
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 8. the palace house is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the futuristic house##1
10. the futuristic house is the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |
| Game          | go     | snooker   | backgammon     |
| Beverage         | fanta | milk   | tea  |
| House           | palace   | ranch-style | futuristic   |
| Color   | chestnut    | emerald       | black    |
| Transport   | taxi        | airplane    | car   |
| Birthday         | june      | march     | september |

 